{"tid":2512031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉改制︱李華明稱清晰收到中共訊息促民主黨參選 中間人提人選意見 黨內9月決定","createTime":"2021-05-01T11:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T11:43:16.000Z","uid":44209,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"7300e7cfe0bebfc9d5da48fc065e7b33f61f7a0a","tid":2512031,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"涉修改香港選舉制度的法例正在立法會審議，日後參選人須取得選委會5大界別提名，外間關注民主派會否派人參選。民主黨前立法會議員李華明接受建制派傳媒《堅雜誌》訪問時，<strong><span class=\"red\">承認清晰收到中共以不同渠道向民主黨中人發訊息，「表示希望民主黨去選，甚至民主黨誰去選，他們都提出了意見。」</span></strong>李向《蘋果》表示，該黨正就是否參選各自表達意見，會留待9月中委會作最後決定。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/R6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FR6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=dfa6a922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FR6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE%2F&h=064cbed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/R6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE/</a>"},{"pid":"9356c25e54771b21cfb17ea0859a4ff1594d2aa7","tid":2512031,"uid":64103,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"終於唔使做民建聯b隊<br />\n正正式式投共"},{"pid":"20963dcffe2745ea9fd24a74d4971142def537cd","tid":2512031,"uid":10200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"中共座上客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3e74c695e2cf0fbfef3d9d6bd22737f750d051","tid":2512031,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9356c25e54771b21cfb17ea0859a4ff1594d2aa7","tid":2512031,"uid":64103,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"